---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Voidless Smith">
  <h2>Voidless Smith</h2>
  <p>The official mod-authoring tool for crafting custom weapons and mods.</p>
  <section>
    <h3>Features</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Mix and match blades, guards, hilts, and pommels.</li>
      <li>Tint parts with HSV or RGB sliders and save palettes.</li>
      <li>Export sprite sheets and JSON configs for immediate use.</li>
      <li>Future updates add one-click mod packaging and Steam Workshop support.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
